Mhleli bengisebenza enkampanini yonogada u-Enforce enganyelwe uNcube oshadelwe nguNgqongqoshe uNomusa Dube-Ncube (osesithombeni). Okubuhlungu basinqamulele izinkontilela ngaphandle kokusazisa njengabasebenzi. Sathatha udaba lwethu saluphonsa kwinyunyana iSatawu, sabe sesiba nomhlangano nayo eyasitshela kuwona ukuthi udaba lwethu luphethwe esifundazweni. Kuthe kungakapheli ngisho isonto sezwa ngamahlebezi ukuthi iSatawu icala isilisulile ngaphandle kokuxhumana nathi. Lokho kungikhombise ukuthi kuleli likaMthayiya kubuswa ngemali nenkohlakalo kusetshenziswa igazi lethu. Lokhu sekungilahlise ithemba ngezwe lethu futhi-ke ngibonile ukuthi lezi zinyunyana ezidla bhodwe linye nale nhlangano ebusayo kumele ungazithembi yizigebengu ezikhonze imali nokugwazelwa.  Senzo Ndlovu